ActNunavut Act
SubjectTransfer to the Commissioner of Nunavut (.0533 hectares)
PrecisOrder transfering to the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, the administration and control of a surveyed parcel of land comprising the bed of a body of water within a pond (approximatively .533 hectares), within the municipal boundaries of the City of Iqualuit.
